| | | | | | | 3 | Hapus isi lama dan tulis isi baru | | | |
| | | | | | | 4 | Klik tombol "Simpan Perubahan" | Jurnal diperbarui dan tampil label "(Diedit)" | Pass | - |
| PBI-11 | TC-11-04 | User menghapus jurnal | Positive | User dapat menghapus jurnal dari riwayat | User sudah login, memiliki minimal 1 jurnal | 1 | Buka halaman `/journals` | | | |
| | | | | | | 2 | Klik tombol "Hapus" pada jurnal | | | |
